*Trenutno* sam u gradu. (Currently I'm in the city.)
Ona je *trenutno* zauzeta. (She is currently occupied.)
On u *trenutnom* trenutku nije video šta se dogodilo. (He didn't see what happened at the current moment.)
Nemačka se *trenutno* nalazi na trećem mestu po broju stanovnika. (Germany is currently at the third place in terms of population.)
*Trenutno* smo na putu. (We are currently on the road.)